ate_talk:World_professional_boxing_champions" title="Template talk:World professional boxing champions"><abbr title="Discuss this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">t</abbr></a></li><li class="nv-edit"><a href="/wiki/Special:EditPage/Template:World_professional_boxing_champions" title="Special:EditPage/Template:World professional boxing champions"><abbr title="Edit this template" style=";;background:none transparent;border:none;box-shadow:none;padding:0;">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id="World_professional_boxing_champions" style="font-size:114%;margin:0 4em"><a href="/wiki/List_of_current_world_boxing_champions" title="List of current world boxing champions">World professional boxing champions</a></div></th></tr><tr><td class="navbox-abovebelow" colspan="2"><div>
